Change Log
-----------

Version 2.0
-----------
*list coming soon*

Version 1.4.1
-------------
1) Fixed a bug with showing Slashdot


Version 1.4
-----------
1) Added Atom feed support (therefore fixing enhancement 21)
2) Changed system to only show the splash screen for a second and then show the interface with a ProgressHUD, like in version 0.5.
3) Fixed defect 9 (mobile-rss just doesn't open sometime) (users please verify)
4) Inserted temp hack for defect 10 (Engadget Feed doesn't show entire article) (see defect for more info)
5) Fixed defect 22 (Edit or add feed no longer functions)
6) Misc other fixes and tweaks


Version 1.3
-----------
1) Auto converts feed:// to http://
2) Added support for Yahoo's feed layout
3) Fixed bug where certain feeds (aka: Slashdot) wouldn't show the feed name under item view
4) Fixed it so if the feed doesn't contain text for an item, the app doesn't crash and instead tells the user that no text was supplied and to click the visit link to see the item.


Version 1.0
-----------
1) Complete Code Rewrite
	a) Faster speeds
	b) Better memory management
	c) Cleaner code
	e) Lots of comments
	f) etc
2) Multiple Feed Support
3) Increased Support for non-standard RSS Feeds
4) Splash Screen


Version 0.5.1
-------------
Fixed bug in program startup that caused a crash if you didn't have a valid feed plist


Version 0.5
-----------
Initial release
